{"word":"ἀναζάω","slug":"ἀναζάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀναζάω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a></el>, *<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ζάω\">ζάω</a></el>] on force of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a></el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a></el> 4. <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘return to life after a state of death’, <b><i>be alive again, return to life</i></b> of Christ <b><a href='B:520 14:9'>Ro 14:9</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>,</b> in imagery <b><a href='B:490 15:24'>Lk 15:24</a>, <a href='B:490 15:32'>32</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘come out of a dormant state’, of sin revived in power, <b><i>come to life, come alive</i> <a href='B:520 7:9'>Ro 7:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀναδίδωμι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀναζητέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}